<%-layout('layouts/boilerplate.ejs') -%>
<body>
    <div class="policy-container">
        <h1 class="main-title">Our Seller Policy</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          Welcome to <strong>SwapNest!</strong> As a seller on our platform, you agree to follow the guidelines outlined below to ensure a safe, transparent, and trustworthy marketplace for all users.
        </p>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>1. Eligibility to Sell</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Must be 18+ years or have parental consent.</li>
            <li>Provide accurate personal and contact details.</li>
            <li>Illegal, counterfeit, or stolen items are strictly prohibited.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>2. Listing Guidelines</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>List only items you own.</li>
            <li>Use clear, unedited photos of the actual item.</li>
            <li>Honest and clear product titles and descriptions.</li>
            <li>Reasonable pricing reflecting item condition.</li>
            <li>Proper categorization is mandatory.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>3. Prohibited Items</h2>
          <p>SwapNest does <strong>not</strong> allow the sale of:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Illegal or stolen goods.</li>
            <li>Drugs, weapons, hazardous materials.</li>
            <li>Alcohol, tobacco, vape products.</li>
            <li>Fake or replica items.</li>
            <li>Obscene or adult content.</li>
            <li>Animals or wildlife-derived products.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>4. Transaction Policies</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Use SwapNest platform for all transactions.</li>
            <li>Ship/deliver items promptly and securely.</li>
            <li>Respond to buyer queries within 24–48 hours.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>5. Condition and Honesty</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Clearly state item condition (New, Like New, Good, Fair, As-Is).</li>
            <li>Disclose any defects or damages upfront.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>6. Pricing and Fees</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Platform may deduct service fees/commissions.</li>
            <li>Include applicable delivery or transaction fees in the price.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>7. Shipping and Delivery</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Package items securely for safe delivery.</li>
            <li>Provide tracking info if available.</li>
            <li>Local pickups must be safe and coordinated professionally.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>8. Cancellations & Returns</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>State return/cancellation policies clearly.</li>
            <li>SwapNest mediates disputes; final decisions are binding.</li>
            <li>Cooperate with buyers during complaint resolution.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>9. Account Suspension</h2>
          <p>Accounts may be suspended for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Repeated policy violations.</li>
            <li>Fraud or scams.</li>
            <li>Abusive or unprofessional conduct.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>10. Legal Compliance</h2>
          <p>Sellers are fully responsible for obeying all applicable local laws, taxes, and safety standards.</p>
        </div>
    
        <div class="policy-block">
          <h2>11. Changes to Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy. Continued use of the platform indicates your acceptance of the new terms.</p>
        </div>
    
        <div class="closing-message">
          <strong>Thank you for being a part of SwapNest. Let’s build a trusted marketplace together!</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
</body>